name: INSearchForMessagesIntentResponseCode
desc: Constants that indicate the response state.

items.name: case ready
items.desc: A response code indicating app readiness.

items.name: case inProgress
items.desc: You are performing the search but do not yet have the results.

items.name: case failure
items.desc: You are unable to perform the search.

items.name: case failureRequiringAppLaunch
items.desc: The user must launch your app to search their messages.

items.name: case failureMessageServiceNotAvailable
items.desc: You were unable to perform the search because your message service is currently unavailable.

items.name: case failureMessageTooManyResults
items.desc: Too many messages matched the specified search criteria.
